highlights.text: “Parayuvaan - From "Ishq"” by Sid Sriram, Neha S. Nair, and Jakes Bejoy has been on Top Songs Kochi the longest, at 62 weeks straight.
“Mockingbird” by Eminem is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kochi, up 14 spots at #31.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Kochi. “Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam")” is the highest at #1.
“Unakkul Naane” by Pritt and dilushselva is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kochi at #48.
